{"claim_id": "claim_003", "text": "Asari uses statistics guided peak detection based on local maxima and prominence with selective use of smoothing.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Statistics guided peak dection, based on local maxima and prominence, selective use of smoothing", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [324, 420], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": ["SYS_ASARI"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_010", "text": "Peak detection is performed on the composite mass tracks to generate a feature list for the experiment.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Peak detection is performed on the composite mass tracks to generate a feature list for the experiment.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [1268, 1370], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_025", "text": "Landmark peak prominence must be greater than 20% of peak height.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "prominence > 20% of peak height", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [3807, 3839], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_030", "text": "If the max intensity of a mass track is higher than 1E8, the mass track is rescaled under 1E8 for peak detection.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "If the max intensity of a mass track is higher that a preset ceiling (1E8), the mass track is rescaled under the preset ceiling for the purpose of peak detection.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5025, 5153], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "data", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000006", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_031", "text": "The default min_intensity_threshold for low-intensity tracks is 1e3 for Orbitrap data.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "If the median intensity on a mass track is below the preset min_intensity_threshold (default 1e3 for Orbitrap data), this is a low-intensity track.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5257, 5403], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "data", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000006", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": ["PARAM_MIN_INTENSITY_THRESHOLD"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_033", "text": "Smoothing is applied when the noise level is higher than 1% of max intensity and max intensity is lower than 10 times of the preset min_peak_height.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Smoothing (chromatograms.smooth_moving_average) is applied when the noise level is higher than 1% of max intensity and max intensity is lower than 10 times of the preset min_peak_height.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [5617, 5760], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": ["PARAM_MIN_PEAK_HEIGHT"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_034", "text": "The initial prominence value for peak detection is 1/3 of min_peak_height.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "the initial value is 1/3 of min_peak_height", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [6019, 6062], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": ["PARAM_MIN_PEAK_HEIGHT"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_035", "text": "For high-intensity and high-noise segments, prominence is set as the greater of prominence and 5% of max intensity.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "if the segment is high-intensity and high-noise, the greater of prominence and 5% of max intensity is used as the new prominence.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [6096, 6221], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_036", "text": "The default sliding window size for prominence computation is 25 scans.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The prominence is computed on a sliding window size (default 25 scans).", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_asari/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [6273, 6336], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "data", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000006", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.1038/s41467-023-39889-1", "spine_entity_ids": []}
